# Feature Module Layout

- Keep feature public contracts in `component/*Component.kt` and `model/*State|Action.kt`.
- Keep feature DI entrypoints in `di/*Module.kt`.
- Keep shared runtime abstractions in `kmp/feature/base`, not per-feature utility files.
- If bridge exposure is needed, annotate interface-level API in `component`.
- Feature module build files should only depend on `kmp/domain`, `kmp/feature/base`, and bridge annotations unless justified.
